 ballasted from final disport Gizan previous voy and been about a week early, but decided instead to take a reload cargo from Gizan up to Sohar.\n\nWith some delay for loading the previous voyage Shell indicated their displeasure at our opportunistic approach. Moreover, situation was exacerbated with Shell informing they were having a tank top situation in Ras Laffan in the middle of the laycan and put the blame on us for this becoming a problem for them. After rattling their sabre about breach of contract we offered the Stena Imperator to alleviate their tank top situation splitting the quantity of nomination. The voyage was never going be a winner but this had a further negative impact on the result, although we did retain the quantity for boosting the Imperator result."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-02-24T14:32:40.747","modifiedByFull":"Leireng, Thomas","remark":"Port Allan FDA and tugs updated"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-01-05T12:58:32.19","modifiedByFull":"Eden, Peter","remark":"have removed Insurance revenue USD 16,394.00 as this cost was both \u0022rebilled\u0022 from expenses and created separately as revenue"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-12-16T20:46:13.54","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"actual bunkers received Houston updated"},{"modifiedDate":"2022-12-13T07:05:10.6","modifiedByFull":"Leireng, Thomas","remark":"Port costs updated and demurrage estimate updated."},{"modifiedDate":"2022-12-06T22:26:15.727","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"tc chems added at Houston - bunker stem added Houston"}],"offhireList":[{"id":193542,"dateStartUtc":null,"dateEndUtc":null,"days":null,"displayOrder":0,"offhireReason":null,"remark":null,"offhireBunkerList":[{"id":135449,"gradeName":"LSBF","quantity":null,"price":null,"displayOrder":0}]}],"tcNumber":null,"tcOutIdEncrypted":null,"tcReletDetail":null}